<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 12:27:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>沙特王储不会出席俄罗斯金砖国家峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/saudis-mbs-will-not-attend-russias-brics-summit-2024-10-10/</link><description>据克里姆林宫称，沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼预计不会出席本月晚些时候由俄罗斯主办的金砖国家峰会，并表示世界最大石油出口国将由沙特外交部长代表。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 12:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/saudis-mbs-will-not-attend-russias-brics-summit-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚3-1战胜中国开启波波维奇时代</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-start-popovic-era-with-3-1-win-over-china-2024-10-10/</link><description>周四，托尼·波波维奇作为澳大利亚队主教练在阿德莱德椭圆形球场举行的世界杯预选赛中以 3-1 战胜中国队，取得了胜利的开局。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:59:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-start-popovic-era-with-3-1-win-over-china-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>宜家呼吁中国采取更多刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-calls-more-china-stimulus-measures-2024-10-10/</link><description>在中国政府宣布一揽子措施以重振遭受房地产危机打击的经济后，瑞典家具零售商宜家周四呼吁中国采取进一步的刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-calls-more-china-stimulus-measures-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>房地产市场疲软降价后宜家销售额下降 5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-sales-fall-5-after-price-cuts-amid-weak-housing-market-2024-10-10/</link><description>瑞典廉价家居用品零售商宜家为了吸引更多购物者并维持其在不断萎缩的家居市场中的份额而降价，该公司的年销售额下降了 5%，但预计明年将出现复苏。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-sales-fall-5-after-price-cuts-amid-weak-housing-market-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>莱尼将向德国政府提交中国股权出售案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-ministry-review-leoni-share-sale-chinese-firm-wiwo-reports-2024-10-10/</link><description>汽车供应商莱尼 (Leoni) 发言人周四表示，该公司正准备向德国政府登记将其多数股权出售给中国公司立讯精密 (Luxshare)，这被称为例行步骤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 10:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-ministry-review-leoni-share-sale-chinese-firm-wiwo-reports-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行原副行长因受贿被判死刑缓期执行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-deputy-central-bank-head-gets-suspended-death-sentence-taking-2024-10-10/</link><description>官方媒体周四称，在金融业开展全面反腐运动之际，中国前央行副行长范一飞因受贿罪被判处死刑，缓期两年执行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 09:53:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-deputy-central-bank-head-gets-suspended-death-sentence-taking-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国因向台湾出售武器而对3家美国公司和10名高级管理人员实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-slaps-sanctions-3-us-firms-10-senior-execs-over-weapons-sales-taiwan-2024-10-10/</link><description>中国外交部周四宣布，因美国向台湾出售武器而对三家与美国军方有联系的公司和十名高级管理人员实施制裁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 09:21:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-slaps-sanctions-3-us-firms-10-senior-execs-over-weapons-sales-taiwan-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>总理称中国将于年底前取消对澳大利亚龙虾的进口禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-lift-ban-australian-lobster-imports-by-year-end-says-pm-2024-10-10/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞周四表示，中国将在年底前恢复进口澳大利亚龙虾，这标志着长达四年的外交斗争的结束，这场斗争导致澳大利亚数百亿美元的出口被禁止进入中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 08:55:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-lift-ban-australian-lobster-imports-by-year-end-says-pm-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>秘书长称东盟在地区紧张局势中发挥“稳定”作用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-plays-stabilising-role-regional-tensions-secretary-general-says-2024-10-10/</link><description>东盟秘书长表示，尽管在缅甸内战和起草南海行为准则等关键问题上仅取得渐进进展，但东盟集团仍然是东南亚的“稳定力量”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 08:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-plays-stabilising-role-regional-tensions-secretary-general-says-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>随着全球需求降温，中国九月出口可能进一步放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-further-september-global-demand-cools-2024-10-10/</link><description>9月份中国出口增速可能为五个月来最慢，这表明制造商不再在几个贸易伙伴征收关税之前急于发出订单，而且全球对中国商品的需求正在疲软。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 08:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-further-september-global-demand-cools-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾呼吁中国和东盟紧急谈判南海规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-calls-urgency-china-asean-negotiating-south-china-sea-code-2024-10-10/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯在周四的区域峰会上敦促东南亚领导人和中国紧急加快南海行为准则谈判，同时指责北京进行骚扰和恐吓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 07:56:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-calls-urgency-china-asean-negotiating-south-china-sea-code-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>袭击发生后中国将与巴基斯坦合作保护中国人员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-work-with-pakistan-protect-chinese-personnel-following-attack-2024-10-10/</link><description>周日，一个分裂主义武装组织声称杀害了两名中国工程师，中国周四表示，将与巴基斯坦合作，保护在巴基斯坦的中国人员、项目和机构的安全。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 07:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-work-with-pakistan-protect-chinese-personnel-following-attack-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>宝马和梅赛德斯季度销量因中国疲软而下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-q3-sales-fall-13-weighed-by-china-delivery-stops-2024-10-10/</link><description>德国豪华汽车制造商周四表示，中国需求疲软和激烈竞争影响了宝马和梅赛德斯第三季度的销量。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 07:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-q3-sales-fall-13-weighed-by-china-delivery-stops-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国奇瑞在西方竞争对手腾出的俄罗斯工厂组装汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-assembles-cars-russian-plants-vacated-by-western-rivals-2024-10-10/</link><description>自入侵乌克兰以来，北京在俄罗斯不断变化的制造业格局和经济中发挥着越来越有影响力的作用。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-assembles-cars-russian-plants-vacated-by-western-rivals-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中概股盛会重启，关注周六</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-10/</link><description>Ankur Banerjee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 04:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>